snippet.title: Horror Tycoon - Official Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Build. Scare. Kill. Repeat. 

Build your own haunted house of horrors!

Scare your guests to gain money and reputation. 

Kill your guests to fulfill contacts with the devil.

Repeat or burn in hell for eternity! 

Official Website: 
www.horrortycoon.com 

For development news, participate in the game development via Discord: https://discord.gg/d7TWSVs
